---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { profile } from '../data/profile';
---

<Layout title="About & Leadership">
    <section class="about-hero fade-in">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>About & Leadership</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Software Development Team Leader | Strategic Leader | AI Innovator</p>
            </div>
            {profile.links.avatar && (
                <div class="profile-image-container">
                    <img src={profile.links.avatar} alt={profile.name} class="profile-image" />
                </div>
            )}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission fade-in delay-1">
        <h2>[MISSION]</h2>
        <p>
            My mission is to build and scale high-performing engineering teams that deliver exceptional value through technical excellence and strategic alignment. With over 9 years of experience, I bridge the gap between complex technical challenges and business objectives, fostering an environment where innovation and efficiency coexist.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="leadership-philosophy fade-in delay-2">
        <h2>[LEADERSHIP_PHILOSOPHY]</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Empowerment</h3>
                <p>I believe in hiring great people and giving them the autonomy, tools, and support they need to succeed. Leadership is about removing roadblocks, not micromanagement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Continuous Excellence</h3>
                <p>From TDD and clean architecture to modern CI/CD, I advocate for high engineering standards that ensure long-term maintainability and system reliability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Adaptability</h3>
                <p>In a rapidly evolving landscape—now accelerated by Agentic AI—the ability to pivot and integrate new frameworks is what separates surviving teams from thriving ones.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="technical-leadership fade-in delay-3">
        <h2>[TECHNICAL_EXPERTISE]</h2>
        <p>
            My leadership approach is grounded in a deep technical foundation across the full stack. I specialize in:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Legacy Evolution:</strong> Strategically migrating monolithic systems to modern, containerized architectures (Docker, AWS).</li>
            <li><strong>Engineering Velocity:</strong> Optimizing development lifecycles through automated workflows and AI-assisted coding frameworks.</li>
            <li><strong>Agile Delivery:</strong> Directing cross-functional teams to deliver enterprise-grade features on time and within budget.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="team-building fade-in">
        <h2>[TEAM_METRICS]</h2>
        <p>
            I currently manage a team of 6+ software engineers at Paycom, where I focus on technical coaching, career development, and building a culture of mutual respect and shared ownership. I believe a team's strength lies in its diversity of thought and its ability to communicate openly.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="beyond-code fade-in">
        <h2>[BEYOND_THE_CODE]</h2>
        <p>
            When I'm not leading engineering initiatives, I explore the intersection of LLMs and developer productivity. Based in Frisco, Texas, I am an advocate for the local tech community and a lifelong learner, originally holding a degree in Mechanical Engineering from Texas A&M University.
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    section { margin-top: 5rem; }
    .hero-content { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3rem; justify-content: space-between; }
    .hero-text { flex: 1; }

    .profile-image-container {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 180px;
        height: 180px;
        border-radius: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.2);
        transform: rotate(-2deg);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(0.8) contrast(1.2);
    }

    .profile-image-container:hover {
        transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.05);
        filter: none;
        border-color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .profile-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero-content { flex-direction: column-reverse; gap: 2rem; align-items: flex-start; }
        .profile-image-container { width: 140px; height: 140px; }
    }

    h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--secondary-text); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }
    
    h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-color); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    
    p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-color); opacity: 0.9; max-width: 800px; }
    
    .values-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    }

    .value-card {
        background: rgba(0, 59, 0, 0.05);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 0;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .value-card:hover { 
        border-color: var(--accent-color);
        background: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.05);
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1);
    }

    .value-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--accent-color); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .value-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; color: var(--text-color); opacity: 0.8; }

    ul { margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; list-style-type: "> "; }
    li { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-color); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.9; }
    li strong { color: var(--accent-color); text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.3); }
</style>
